PlugIns/IMDiagnosticExtension.appex/Cont.DELocalizedDataCollectedSummaryText: Messages logging includes collection of an extended age of OS logs as well as statistics to help diagnose unread count and Spotlight issues.
PlugIns/IMDiagnosticExtension.appex/Cont.DELocalizedConsentText: Collected logs may include message and chat identifiers, but will not contain message text.

PlugIns/ScreenTimeDiagnosticExtension.ap.DELocalizedConsentText: Collected logs may include Screen Time settings as well as app and website activity data.

PlugIns/com.apple.DiagnosticExtensions.W.DELocalizedCustomerConsentText: Wi-Fi Logs included in this report may contain personal information about your Wi-Fi connections, including transferred content and nearby Wi-Fi router hardware addresses. It may also contain Bluetooth logs that include sensitive data like phone call history, shared notification content, paired Bluetooth device names, and recently connected or nearby devices. If you're concerned about the included information, you can go back to review or remove it.
PlugIns/com.apple.DiagnosticExtensions.W.WLAN_DELocalizedCustomerConsentText: WLAN Logs included in this report may contain personal information about your WLAN connections, including transferred content and nearby WLAN router hardware addresses. If you're concerned about the included information, you can go back to review or remove it.
